ISPAPI DomainCheck Addon for WHMCS
______________________________________________________________________________

Changelog
______________________________________________________________________________

v 7.3.0 - 2018-XX-XX
 - MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS: ISPAPI Registrar Module v1.0.53 at least
 - complete relaunch of the user interface
 - integration of API Suggestion Engine
 - premium domains support simplified (Premium domains now supported in WHMCS)
 - manual adding of pricing for premium domains no more required, prices are taken from the API, markup can be defined in WHMCS directly
 - removed sub-categories (only 1 level of categories will be displayed)
 - added button to add default categories
 - adding/removing of elements to/from the cart instantly possible in the search results
 - renewal pricing displayed in the search results
 - Language files have been updated

v 7.2.0 - 2017-08-07
 - added whois fallback to WHMCS's DomainLookup when HEXONET's QueryDomainWhoisInfo API command is limited (special case for .CH and .LI)

v 7.1.0 - 2017-07-10
 - added backorder button in the search results (only when ISPAPI Backorder Module is installed)
 - design optimization

v 7.0.0 - 2016-10-10
 - compatible with WHMCS 7.0 or higher
 - compatible with PHP7
 - user interface redesign
 - new README.pdf

v 6.0.6 - 2016-09-16
 - workarround for user that do not have mb_detect_encoding function in PHP

v 6.0.5 - 2016-03-14
 - fixed issue: wrong currency used when customer was logged in

v 6.0.4 - 2016-03-01
 - fix for premium pricing issue

v 6.0.3 - 2015-10-05
 - fixed issue: some users were having a blank page when using the domainchecker

v 6.0.2 - 2015-08-20
 - security vulnerabilities fixed

v 6.0.1 - 2015-07-23
 - domainchecker now responsive
 - premium domains not displayed in the renewal list (will be renewed over the product)

v 6.0.0 - 2015-07-10
 - compatible with WHMCS 6.0.0 or higher (not compatible with 5.x.x)
 - user interface redesign


